     <para>
      During WAL replay, guard against corrupted record lengths exceeding
      1GB (Michael Paquier)
     </para>

     <para>
      Treat such a case as corrupt data.  Previously, the code would try to
      allocate space and get a hard error, making recovery impossible.
     </para>
